concept Shading

purpose
    to manage the shading mode (unlit/lit) and update materials accordingly

state
    a shadingMode String
    a materialProps Object

actions
    toggle (shading: Shading) : (shading: Shading)
    setMode (shading: Shading, mode: String) : (shading: Shading)
    updateMaterials (shading: Shading, props: Object) : (shading: Shading)
